I can&#39;t remember:  Did they ever explain to you why they call you Purple?  Could this be the color of your aura or something?  If so, maybe they really can &quot;see&quot; us and our surroundings, and not just read our minds and see the world through our eyes?



--- In EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com, Frank Sumption &lt;purplealiengirl@...&gt; wrote:
&gt;
&gt;  So far, I have not heard of anyone else being told they are &quot;The Princess&quot;
&gt; or &quot;Purple&quot;, so I think we do have our own groups, plus normal spirits that
