&gt; &gt; to
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; me that would mean something? Or to my friend Heather? We both asked,
&gt; &gt; and
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; got nothing, at least not that we could discern. It would seem a simple
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; thing to say the word plumber (that was my dad&#39;s secret word) or some
&gt; &gt; other
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; single-syllable word. Now I&#39;m pretty sure I really did talk to my dad,
